---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1>About Shicoku / 詩哭</h1>
    <p>
      Shicoku (詩哭) is a personal website dedicated to sharing poetry, art, and
      musings. The name "Shicoku" combines the Japanese words for "poem" (詩)
      and "cry" (哭), reflecting the emotional depth and expressive nature of
      the content shared here.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is built using Astro, a modern web framework that allows for
      fast and optimized web experiences. Feel free to explore the various
      sections and reach out if you have any questions or comments!
    </p>
  </main></Layout
>
